## 3. Payments, Billing & GitHub Sponsors

Ambastha utilizes **GitHub Sponsors** as its primary financial gateway to ensure transparency and security.

- **Transaction Authority:** All payments are processed via GitHub, Inc. Ambastha does not store credit card or bank details.
- **Taxation & Documentation:** Official receipts and tax invoices are issued solely by **GitHub**. Users are responsible for retrieving these documents from their GitHub **Sponsorships** dashboard for their own accounting or tax purposes.
- **Finality:** All sales are **final**. Users accept all currency (USD/INR) volatility risks.
- **1-Hour Window:** Duplicate claims are only valid if occurring within **one (1) hour** of the first transaction. Later payments are considered separate, intentional purchases.
- **Resolution:** Verified duplicates result in **Subscription Extensions**, never monetary refunds.

