## 5. Limitation of Action (Time-Bar)

- **One-Year Limit:** Any legal claim must be filed within **one (1) year** of the incident. Late claims are permanently barred.
- **Post-Deletion Waiver:** Account deletion constitutes a **final settlement**. You waive the right to bring any "revelation" or "coercion" claims after voluntarily deleting your data.

